<geoCoordinate id="4CF150126400F40CFF3FFB4F1226FB09" box="[189,306,1210,1233]" degrees="45" direction="east" minutes="28" orientation="longitude" pageId="3" pageNumber="80" precision="15" seconds="60" value="45.483334">45°28′60″E</geoCoordinate>
], s. dat. [specimen received at P on 
<date id="5D7B10156400F40CFD05FB491022FB09" box="[647,822,1211,1233]" pageId="3" pageNumber="80" value="1919-12-04">
<collectingDate id="4D3FE9FD6400F40CFD05FB491022FB09" box="[647,822,1211,1233]" pageId="3" pageNumber="80" value="1919-12-04">4 December 1919</collectingDate>
</date>
], 
<emphasis id="1BB1EAC76400F40CFCC4FB4910DBFB09" box="[838,975,1212,1233]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">
<collectorName id="843053036400F40CFCC4FB4910B3FB09" box="[838,935,1212,1233]" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">R. Decary</collectorName>
s.n.
</emphasis>
(P00224809!) [reproduced here in 
<figureCitation id="B1FE2A506400F40CFAA0FB4E1648FB09" box="[1314,1372,1211,1233]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="7.[136,229,1991,2013]" captionTargetBox="[217,1371,190,1966]" captionTargetId="figure-17@7.[217,1371,190,1966]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 8. Lectotype of Euphorbia fiha Decary, Decary s.n. (P00224809). Credit: Muséum national d’histoire naturelle, Paris." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6556805" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6556805/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
].
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="61DF655E6400F40CFF0AFAF513F5F97E" pageId="3" pageNumber="80" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="297A36D56400F40CFF0AFAF513F5F97E" blockId="3.[136,1452,1280,1702]" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">
<emphasis id="1BB1EAC76400F40CFF0AFAF513F2FAC2" bold="true" box="[136,230,1280,1306]" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">Note:—</emphasis>
The 
<typeStatus id="F67E88776400F40CFE99FAF51269FAC2" box="[283,381,1280,1306]" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="EEC54D566400F40CFE2BFAF511B0FAC2" box="[425,676,1280,1306]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="3" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="plagiantha">
<emphasis id="1BB1EAC76400F40CFE2BFAF511B0FAC2" box="[425,676,1280,1306]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">Euphorbia plagiantha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is very poor and consists only of dried capsules. We decided here to designate an epitype based on a specimen collected from the type locality (Behara) to ascertain the application of the name. The name 
<taxonomicName id="EEC54D566400F40CFE1EFABC1157FABA" authority="Decary" authorityName="Decary, Decary" authorityYear="1921" box="[412,579,1352,1378]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="3" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fiha">
<emphasis id="1BB1EAC76400F40CFE1EFABC12FDFABA" box="[412,489,1352,1378]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">E. fiha</emphasis>
Decary
</taxonomicName>
was first cited as synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="EEC54D566400F40CFC2BFABC1785FABA" authority="Drake" authorityName="Drake" box="[937,1169,1352,1378]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="3" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="plagiantha">
<emphasis id="1BB1EAC76400F40CFC2BFABC1750FABA" box="[937,1092,1352,1378]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">E. plagiantha</emphasis>
Drake
</taxonomicName>
del Castillo in 
<bibRefCitation id="4D544B246400F40CFAC4FABD120CFA5E" author="Govaerts, R. &amp; Frodin, D. G. &amp; Radcliffe-Smith, A." pageId="3" pageNumber="80" refId="ref1996" refString="Govaerts, R., Frodin, D. G. &amp; Radcliffe-Smith, A. (2000) World checklist and bibliography of Euphorbiaceae (and Pandaceae). The Board of Trustees of the Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew, Richmond, 1622 pp." type="book" year="2000">
Govaerts 
<emphasis id="1BB1EAC76400F40CFF0AFA9813D6FA5E" box="[136,194,1388,1414]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">et al.</emphasis>
(2000)
</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="4D544B246400F40CFEA1FA9912E0FA5E" author="Decary, R." box="[291,500,1388,1414]" pageId="3" pageNumber="80" pagination="5 - 38" refId="ref1819" refString="Decary, R. (1921) Monographie du district de Tsihombe. Bulletin Economique de Madagascar 18: 5 - 38." type="journal article" year="1921">Decary (1921: 21)</bibRefCitation>
did not cite specimens for his description, only a set of localities where the plant is reportedly found (“Tsihombe”, “Narahy”, “ 
<location id="2C1A600E6400F40CFDEAFA65102DFA72" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:A16C87C36400F40CFF0AFBF213F5F97E:2C1A600E6400F40CFDEAFA65102DFA72" box="[616,825,1424,1450]" country="Madagascar" municipality="Decary's" name="North of Ankaboa" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">North of Ankaboa</location>
”, “Ankilitelo”). Of all the specimens available at P by 
<collectorName id="843053036400F40CFA10FA6513CDFA16" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">R. Decary</collectorName>
(
<emphasis id="1BB1EAC76400F40CFF6BFA40107BFA16" box="[233,879,1460,1486]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">Decary s.n., 3370, 3377, 3408, 3760, 4652, 10449, 10678</emphasis>
), only one (
<emphasis id="1BB1EAC76400F40CFC75FA401763FA16" box="[1015,1143,1461,1486]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">Decary s.n.</emphasis>
) predates 1921 (the year of publication of the name) and has been collected in Tsihombe and received at P in 1919. This specimen (reproduced in 
<figureCitation id="B1FE2A506400F40CFF0AFA0913DDF9CE" box="[136,201,1532,1558]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="7.[136,229,1991,2013]" captionTargetBox="[217,1371,190,1966]" captionTargetId="figure-17@7.[217,1371,190,1966]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 8. Lectotype of Euphorbia fiha Decary, Decary s.n. (P00224809). Credit: Muséum national d’histoire naturelle, Paris." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6556805" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6556805/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
) bears an original field label “ 
<taxonomicName id="EEC54D566400F40CFD99FA0911D1F9CE" authorityName="Decary, Decary" authorityYear="1921" box="[539,709,1532,1558]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="3" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fiha">
<emphasis id="1BB1EAC76400F40CFD99FA0911D1F9CE" box="[539,709,1532,1558]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">Euphorbia fiha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(décrit dans 
<collectorName id="843053036400F40CFCD6FA091716F9CF" box="[852,1026,1532,1559]" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">Bull. Ac. Malg.</collectorName>
) Tsihombe”, likely by Decary himself and thus constitutes material he has seen. For this reason 
<emphasis id="1BB1EAC76400F40CFD7DF9D4106AF9E2" box="[767,894,1569,1594]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">Decary s.n.</emphasis>
has to be designated as a 
<typeStatus id="F67E88776400F40CFB1AF9D51616F9E2" box="[1176,1282,1568,1594]" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">lectotype</typeStatus>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="4D544B246400F40CFA89F9D513BAF986" author="Decary, R." pageId="3" pageNumber="80" pagination="5 - 38" refId="ref1819" refString="Decary, R. (1921) Monographie du district de Tsihombe. Bulletin Economique de Madagascar 18: 5 - 38." type="journal article" year="1921">Decary (1921: 21)</bibRefCitation>
mentions that his epithet is derived from plants known in the south of 
<collectingCountry id="51D276456400F40CFC46F9B1175FF986" box="[964,1099,1604,1630]" name="Madagascar" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
under the local name “ 
<taxonomicName id="EEC54D566400F40CFAD2F9B11691F986" authorityName="Decary, Decary" authorityYear="1921" box="[1360,1413,1604,1630]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="3" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fiha">
<emphasis id="1BB1EAC76400F40CFAD2F9B11691F986" box="[1360,1413,1604,1630]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">Fiha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”, a term first mentioned by 
<bibRefCitation id="4D544B246400F40CFE1AF99D116FF95B" author="Poisson, H. L." box="[408,635,1640,1667]" pageId="3" pageNumber="80" refId="ref2346" refString="Poisson, H. L. (1912) Recherches sur la flore meridionale de Madagascar. A. Challamel (Ed.) Librairie maritime et coloniale, Paris, 230 pp." type="book" year="1912">Poisson (1912: 126)</bibRefCitation>
for a yet to describe “Euphorbe” [French for spurge] matching 
<collectingMunicipality id="C91EACAF6400F40CFACAF99D16B8F95A" box="[1352,1452,1640,1666]" pageId="3" pageNumber="80">Decary’s</collectingMunicipality>
species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
